HEADWORD: maul-stick
<hw>maul"-stick`</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G. <ets>malerstock</ets>; <ets>maler</ets> a painter
+ <ets>stock</ets> stick.]</ety> <def>A stick used by painters as a rest
for the hand while working.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>mahl-stick</asp> and <asp>mahlstick</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
